Best Down Dog ever. ü§çü©∂ I would like to thank everyone for the outpouring of love you‚Äôve shown to me and my family as we navigate through life without this big goofy boy. I know I haven‚Äôt responded back to a lot of your DM‚Äôs but it‚Äôs just been so hard. I pretty much run from people these days in public because it‚Äôs just so hard to receive condolences in person. I feel like bursting into tears every time someone hugs me. I want to become a hermit at home‚Ä¶ and yet, don‚Äôt want to be home at all. ü§∑üèª‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è Life continues to just move on I guess.

Today I came home to an empty house. Spent a solid 2 hours at the gym murdering myself to just not feel anything for a moment. Even before opening the house door, it hit me. Does the pain ever even get to a manageable level at any point? I know it‚Äôs only been a day and it‚Äôll take time but there is such a hole where my heart was. I knew the end was inevitable but no one can prepare you for this shit that‚Äôs for sure.

I‚Äôm already apologizing because my content this week will probably be like this. üò≠ 

I will miss making my @aloyoga content with you Thor. #AloPartner (Please don‚Äôt judge me too harshly for this but I still have obligations with my work.)

üåà Dearest Thor, 

My heart is broken. You peacefully passed over the rainbow bridge today surrounded by family. You were my bestest friend‚Ä¶ my little duckling‚Ä¶ my baby bear. Thank you for giving me so much love. I already miss you so much and I‚Äôm not even sure how I will ever not feel sad. Thank you for choosing me to be your mama. And thank you for letting me know at the end that you loved me. Right before you went to sleep, you picked up your head, looked up at me with your beautiful eyes and gave me 2 big kisses before laying your head down in my lap for the final time. You can rest easy now sweet boy. We love you so much and hopefully one day, I‚Äôll see you again. #AllDogsGoToHeaven #FUCKYOUCANCER
